After a week of watching this list, I am inclined to agree with you. My 
company has a similar list with IBM's MVS operating system and IBM's 
AS400 mini (approaching maxi) included.  At the moment I am working 
thoroughly through Jameson's Multi-Platform Code management book and 
ordering other books. Converting his code to OS/2 is teaching me some 
lessons... and he has thought about the problem, and worked on it, for 
some years. 

